    "body": "## Summary\n\n- Moves `deepep_ht_prepare_finalize.py` → `prepare_finalize/deepep_ht.py`\n- Moves `deepep_ll_prepare_finalize.py` → `prepare_finalize/deepep_ll.py`\n- Moves `flashinfer_a2a_prepare_finalize.py` → `prepare_finalize/flashinfer_a2a_prepare_finalize.py`\n- Updates all importers (`all2all_utils.py` and four test files) to use the new paths\n- No functional changes — pure file reorganization\n\nThis is part of the ongoing effort to organize `vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe` kernels into logical subfolders (e.g. `experts/`, `prepare_finalize/`, `router/`, `runner/`).\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] Pre-commit hooks pass (ruff, mypy, SPDX checks) ✅\n- [x] Existing DeepEP and FlashInfer MoE tests continue to pass (no logic changed)\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)",
